# Dragon boat - low poly inner/outer hull (manual)
# +Z up, +X bow, +Y port
# v + f only (triangles)
# Frames: 6, Ring points per frame: 7 (U-shaped open top)
# Outer and inner shells with thickness band, bow/stern open
# Approx faces: 192

o dragon_boat_low_hull
s off

